 This model requires pre-trained word vectors from the GloVe (Global Vectors for Word Representation) website. For the code to run you will need to follow the steps below

1. You will need to download the gloVe data text file for the website[https://nlp.stanford.edu/projects/glove/] the one you want will be under **NEW!!** 2024 Wikipedia + Gigaword 5 (11.9B tokens, 1.2M vocab, uncased, 50d vectors, 290 MB download): 

2. Rename the file to gloVe.txt and make sure to place it here in this  directory